{"tid":1768402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌曬你班休息撚","createTime":"2019-12-04T04:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T06:28:11.000Z","uid":318229,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fadbc59b940bfa061997737145911565f98ce0","tid":1768402,"uid":318229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"黎明行動頭個禮拜不知幾成功 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大專全部停課 完sem 驚撚到得返Online Test交essay <br />\n中小學又停課一個禮拜 <br />\n其實最有效就係 掉嘢落路軌 (坐地鐵真係成效不大) 加上再塞撚住曬啲隧道 只要唔玩陣地 全部快閃 佢搬走完又塞返 未得囉 佢搬嘅同時又可以喺隔離裝修下 6點即刻龜縮返屋企 啲狗趕到黎人影都唔見多隻 都吹你唔漲啦<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個禮拜真係靜到閪咁 熱門一個行動po都冇 大家檢討下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎明行動頭果禮拜係我咁大個人係香港見過最亂嘅一個禮拜 要贏就要堅持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">早睡早起身體好！<strong></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1c10e367a769bc27d7e826a6005445534ca57d83","tid":1768402,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"天氣凍了"},{"pid":"b11815960a9f9e719a35a6421fc98e376b1d496f","tid":1768402,"uid":318229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:49:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"10a2bc80f3a978cb6f0cb6858c8a87ba0439859b","tid":1768402,"uid":318229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:50:05.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"061acadc636ce2d948c8a6575ee467f48d0845a6","tid":1768402,"uid":318229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"12dd91cda63d50175c147128e23a874e03d59310","tid":1768402,"uid":318229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"e5d1a67ad2adb953452fda72fa90dd31e3f4064f","tid":1768402,"uid":318229,"like":0,